metadata.name: A Harmonious Symphony of Nature
metadata.description:
This artwork encourages us to remember our connection with nature, and to appreciate the beauty that surrounds us. It is a reminder that harmony and tranquility can be found simply by living in the present moment and by appreciating simple but beautiful elements like a swan swimming freely through the sunset.
